HEADWORD: Geyserite
<hw>Gey"ser*ite</hw> <pr>(g⟦imac⟧"z⟦etil⟧r*⟦imac⟧t <it>or</it>
g⟦imac⟧"s⟦etil⟧r*⟦imac⟧t; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
